members.member:

Remote PAUSE.

 /// Forced execution not allowed (Remote RUN cannot be executed when other device
executes Remote STOP or Remote PAUSE.)


Remote PAUSE.

/// Forced execution allowed (Remote RUN can be executed when other device
executes Remote STOP or Remote PAUSE.)

member.summary:
            Read multiple values from the server randomly. 


For example:

            - [] bits =  [] {  ("X0"),  ("M10")};
            - [] words =  [] {  ("D0"),  ("SD5"),  ("SD10")};
            - [] dwords =  [] {  ("D20"),  ("SD20")};
            - [] floats =  [] {  ("D30")};
            ReadDeviceRandom(null, words, null, floats);
            ReadDeviceRandom(bits, words, dwords, floats);
